item.title: CVE-2023-0034|2024-08-02T04:54:32.572Z -- unknown -- jetwidgets%20for%20elementor
item.description: The JetWidgets For Elementor WordPress plugin before 1.0.14 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
